name: Gean
description:
Gean....one of her own in the family of Whimsical Children.  Our line of Whimsical Children are original one of a kind children that are to represent a special little one in your life that will be around your neck  on a 18 inch Sterling Silver linked necklace with a S shaped clasp for  a Mother, Grandmother, Aunt or Friend to enjoy.   Whimsical Children will tell you stories...We have created these wonderful children from semi precious stones that can represent the special child in your life. 

You may personally request special child to be made for you using birthstones, and sterling silver or any one stone of your choose that we have available at the time; just simply give us a call at 1-931-259-6714 and we will be glad to assist you in designing your own Whimsical Child. item#GW
